extendedInfo.description: Courtney Cass Facebook Fan Page NOW UP!!http://www.facebook.com/pages/Courtney-Cass/117473158321736I am just a regular chick trying to do big things ;) I did things kinda backwards...had a good job in sales, received 2 college degrees in Business & Criminal Justice (Law was the original plan from there), quit my job, and decided to live my dream...you only live once :)I am a full-time, professional print and spokesmodel, and I do some acting work here (theatre & film) and there...contact me for full, professional resume & stats....Where you can see me:-Playboy TV's "The Boy Nexxt Door" Season 2, Episode 2.-2008 Budweiser Commercial-INFO Magazine - Milwaukee (March 09')- CD cover and inside art for band "Tango Down"-Performance Boats Magazine Model www.performanceboats.com-F/X Fashions Swimsuit model.-Glamour/Art Nude Photography workshops for Rolando Gomez (St. Thomas, U.S.V.I. 08'), Bill Lemon (Portland, OR 08"), GW Burns (St. Louis, MO 08').-Gallery Installations for Artists around the country (Cid Nowosad www.cidnowosad.com, Kevin Beilfuss www.kevinbeilfuss.com, Taradji).-An illustrated adaptation of the pulp classic "The Spider's Novel, The Devil's Paycheck".-Cardow Jewelers (Virgin Islands Jeweler)-The film "Not Another B Movie", appearing with Larry Thomas (Seinfeld's "Soup Nazi), Ed Asner, & David Faustino (Married with Children's "Bud").just to name a few.... ;)While I currently reside in the Chicago area, I travel a LOT, so I am usually not sleeping in my own bed...or this state, for that matter, a good portion of the time. I am also a liquor model, market manager, & event manager for several brands and agencies, including:JamesonMalibu Ultimat VodkaAbsolutCoors LightBlue MoonLucid AbsinthePatronUV VodkaFeckin Irish WhiskeyLe Tourment Vert AbsintheHornitos TequilaNewcastle BeerFrangelicoThree Olives Vodkaand a ton of others...When I am not working, I try to spend as much time with my poochie & my peeps, as possible....yes, I still LOVE to shop!!! :) Love the beach and try to stay away from the cold Winters of Chicago as much as possible. Love my pooch Max, and he is spoiled to death!! I am also an aunt and have the CUTEST nephews in the world!! :DSo, that is me in a nutshell, I suppose....I work a lot, live a pretty crazy, all over the place life, but I would not trade it for anything and have no complaints....live today like you have no tomorrow, and live your dreams, rather than dream them! :)In order to give you a free app and keep developing more free apps in the future, we are integrating a search tool to our application. This will add a few access points to your device (hence the permissions) to direct you to the web search service. Please consider using the search to help us keep creating apps. You may delete the search icon, bookmark and homepage easily. Thank you.
